# Prosperity loot-detail panel — 9-slice frame (slice inset = 12px)
# Neutral slate frame with treasure-gold corner accents. Tier color is a
# programmatic accent; the centered chest watermark is drawn in code
# (a 9-slice center is stretched, so it cannot be baked here).
